agenttool (0.2.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  * Initial release on Debian/Ubuntu.
  * Terminal-based agentic coding assistant powered by local LLMs.
  * Supports Ollama and LM Studio model discovery.
  * Tool-calling loop with web search, file I/O, and shell execution.

